; Coverage for xact.cc lines 1092-1103 ($variable substitution in auto_xact)
; When an auto transaction account contains $variable, the variable is
; resolved from the matching post's scope.

= Expenses
    (Budget:$account)    -1

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Budget
24-Jan-01 Test                  (Budget:Expenses:Food)      $-10.00      $-10.00
end test
